--- a/CLAUDE.md
+++ b/CLAUDE.md
@@ -58,3 +58,9 @@ tests/
 - Uses UV package manager, not pip
 - launchd plist is `com.rickarmbrust.things-agent` (not `alfred`)
 - Port 8200 chosen to avoid conflict with sherlock-hq (8300) and things-mcp (8100)
+- Health endpoint is `/api/v1/health` (not `/health`) — router prefix applies
+- Two launchd services: `things-agent` (FastAPI on 8200) and `things-bot` (Telegram polling)
+- Watchdog (`com.rickarmbrust.things-mcp-watchdog`) checks health every 10 min, restarts things-mcp + things-bot on failure
+- Daily restart (`com.rickarmbrust.things-mcp-restart`) restarts both at 4 AM to prevent stale processes
+- Logs: `logs/stdout.log` / `logs/stderr.log` (API), `logs/bot-stderr.log` (bot)
+- things-mcp can lose SQLite database access after long uptime — watchdog handles this automatically
